Title: The Endless Conflict
Description:
<You notice a book beside the body of a Great Glorious Alliance soldier.

Quickly flicking through the pages, you see that it's some type of journal. 

Parts of it were ruined by a puddle of oil.

Soridormi will want to see this.>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Oil-Soaked Log Book to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return the item to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
